title: SMC_CAMSWITCH_TOGGLE_EVENTS (Struct)
text:
TYPE SMC_CAMSWITCH_TOGGLE_EVENTS : STRUCT
The list of future toggle events of
SMC_DigitalCamSwitch_HighPrecision

rows.Name: a
rows.Comment:
Array of future toggle events, sorted in ascending order by
the switching time.

rows.Name: numEvents
rows.Comment: Number of toggle events stored in the array.
